citations:
    citation-agot-jon-vii:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Jon VII"
            text_from_source: "Hear my words, and bear witness to my vow. Night gathers, and now my watch begins. It shall not end until my death. I shall take no wife, hold no lands, father no children. I shall wear no crowns and win no glory. I shall live and die at my post."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Jon Snow and Samwell Tarly take their Night's Watch vows before a circle of nine weirwood trees beyond the Wall. Sam chooses to take his vows at the heart tree with Jon. Jon is assigned as Mormont's personal steward. Assignments: Jon and Sam to stewards, Grenn/Pyp/Matthar/Todder to rangers, Halder/Albett to builders, Dareon to stewards (Eastwatch). Ghost retrieves a severed human hand from the woods."
